quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  54,1,"Darngal ngal ɓadike, lewru ndun kadi seekike"
  54,2,"Si ɓe yi'ii maande, ɓe ɗuurnoo ɓe wi'a: \"Ko mbilewu jokkondirngu"
  54,3,"Ɓe fenni, ɓe jokki mbeleeɗe maɓɓe. Hara le huunde kala no mari ñiiɓirde"
  54,4,"Gomɗii kumpite arii e maɓɓe, ɗe haɗitorɗum woni e mun"
  54,5,"[Ɗum] ko ñeñƴal yottiingal. Kono jertingol ngol nafaali"
  54,6,Selu ɓe. Ñalnde noddoowo on noddoyta e huunde añiniinde
  54,7,"jaasuɓe ndaarɗe, hiɓe yaltira e genaale ɗen wano kanuuji caratooɗi"
  54,8,"heñaniiɓe noddoowo on. Heeferɓe ɓen wi'a: \"Ndee ko ñalaande sattunde"
  54,9,"Ado maɓɓe, yimɓe nuuhu ɓen yedduno. Ɓe fenni jeyaaɗo Amen on, ɓe wi'i : \"Ko jinnaaɗo!\", o kammbanaa"
  54,10,"O torii Joomi makko, wonnde : \"Min on ko mi foolaaɗo, faabo [lam]"
  54,11,"Men udditiri dammbuɗe kammu ngun, ndiyam wanncoojam"
  54,12,Men fuccitiri leydi ndin ɓulli. Ndiye ɗen fottiri e yamiroore hoddiranoonde
  54,13,"Men roondori mo e [laana] lesaaka marka alluwe e peŋe"
  54,14,"hika dogira e ndenka Amen. Ɗum ko njoɓdi [Nuuhu] fennanooɗo on. @Corrected"
  54,15,"Gomɗii Men accirii [kon ko Men waɗi ɓe] tasakuyee. Taw si woodi waajitorayɗo"
  54,16,Taskii ko honno lepte Am e jertinol (Am) wa'unoo
  54,17,Gomɗii Men newinirii Alqur'aanare nden waajitorgol. Hara wooday waajitorɗo
  54,18,Aadi'en fennuno. Taskee ko honno lepte Am e jertinol (Am) wa'unoo
  54,19,"Men wurtu e maɓɓe henndu sattundu, e ñalaande hiitaande, duumiinde"
  54,20,"hindu wippitira yimɓe ɓen, wa si tawii ko ɓe daƴƴe tamaro irtaaɗe"
  54,21,Taskee ko honno lepte Am ɗen e jertinol (Am) ngol wa'unoo
  54,22,Gomɗii Men newinirii Alqur'aanare nden sabu waajitorgol. Hara wooday waajitorɗo